iptablesbuild installation instructions:

Basic Installation:

perl install.pl


Advanced options (for install.pl):
--conf - Defines the Configuration directory (Default is /etc
--bin - Defines the place to put the Binaries (Default is /usr/sbin)
--perl - Defines the location of the perl binary (Default is /usr/bin/perl)
--docs - Defines where to place the domumentation for iptablesbuild into (Default is /usr/share/doc)
--root - Defines a chroot directory to install into (Default is /)



